#compdef cargo-do
# Documentation: https://github.com/pwoolcoc/cargo-do
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# cargo-do: run multiple comma-separated cargo subcommands in one invocation.
# Upstream README documents no CLI flags; only positional comma-separated commands.

_arguments -s -S \
  '*::comma_separated_cargo_invocations:' && return 0
